      "message": "Patch Set 4: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\n(23 inline comments)\n\nMajor issue here is the network protocol changes that are not well defined or explained.  At least a comment block describing the structure of the packed updates is needed, along with moving all of the wire protocol structures to lustre_idl.h.",
